Your `SetupTests.cs` has exactly the issue on **line 13** — `context.TestName` inside `[ClassInitialize]`. Here's the fix — move the access to `[TestInitialize]`:

```csharp
[ClassInitialize]
public static void ClassInit(TestContext context)
{
    // Class-level setup only (no per-test properties here)
}

[TestInitialize]
public void TestInit()
{
    var testName = TestContext.TestName;
    // Log setup for specific test
}
```

